HEADWORD: Comptible
<hw>Compt"i*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Compt</er>, <pos>v. t.</pos>]</ety> <def>Accountable; responsible;
sensitive.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I am very <qex>comptible</qex> even to the least sinister
usage.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Comptly</ent>⟦br⟧
